  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "We use maximum sequence length of 512 tokens.",
    "Software In our implementations, we use LangChain (LangChain, 2025), Huggingface Transformers (Wolf et al., 2020), and faiss-cpu (Yamaguchi, 2025).",
    "All our experiments are executed on NVIDIA A100 GPUs with 80GB of memory.",
    "We use the following hyperparameters across all experiments: the number of retrieved passages is fixed at k = 10 for all datasets, consistent with the official evaluation settings of both HotpotQA and MultiHop-RAG.",
    "Both sub-query generation and answer synthesis are performed with a sampling temperature of 0.8; and we apply nucleus sampling with Top-p = 0.8."
  ],
